%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic%20purposely%20made%20its%20new%20Mythos-based%20models%20bad%20at%20AI%20research%2C%20and%20developers%20are%20fuming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic's%20Co-Founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20Dario%20Amodei%20on%20stage%20at%20the%20Code%20with%20Claude%20developer%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1daf772ab5f9757add78b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20in%20May.%3Cp%3EDon%20Feria%2FAP%20Content%20Services%20for%20Anthropic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic's%20new%20Mythos-based%20models%20purposely%20limit%20AI%20research%20outputs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20experts%20are%20criticizing%20Anthropic%20for%20these%20subtle%20limitations%20on%20user%20assistance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20reignites%20debate%20over%20why%20Anthropic%20delayed%20Mythos%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20powerful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-anthropic-ai-coding-database-intent-samuel-colvin-pydantic-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20deliberately%20become%20less%20helpful%20when%20they%20detect%20users%20are%20working%20on%20AI%20research%2C%20according%20to%20technical%20disclosures%20that%20are%20already%20sparking%20controversy%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-cdn.anthropic.com%2Fd00db56fa754a1b115b6dd7cb2e3c342ee809620.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esystem%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-fable-5-mythos-class-model-release-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMythos%205%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Fable%205%20published%20Tuesday%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20limited%20the%20models'%20usefulness%20for%20tasks%20related%20to%20developing%20frontier%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20measures%20stem%20from%20concerns%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-pause-reactions-response-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20AI%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20accelerate%20the%20development%20of%20competing%20models%20without%20equivalent%20safety%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20safeguards%20used%20for%20cybersecurity%2C%20biology%2C%20or%20chemistry-related%20risks%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20these%20interventions%20are%20intentionally%20invisible%20to%20users.%20Rather%20than%20refusing%20requests%20or%20switching%20to%20another%20model%2C%20Mythos%20may%20subtly%20modify%20its%20responses%20through%20techniques%20such%20as%20altering%20user%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20was%20swiftly%20criticized%20by%20some%20AI%20experts%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20especially%20the%20idea%20that%20Anthropic%20designed%20models%20that%20purposely%20withhold%20information%20or%20provide%20degraded%20assistance%20without%20users'%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnthropic's%20latest%20model%20will%20NOT%20help%20you%20if%20it%20thinks%20your%20ML%20research%2FML%20engineering%20is%20interesting%2C%20and%2For%20will%20secretly%20degrade%20its%20IQ%20so%20that%20the%20average%20engineer%20won't%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20AI%20research%20firm%20SemiAnalysis%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20referring%20to%20machine%20learning%2C%20a%20type%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20already%20seeing%20Anthropic's%20latest%20model's%20moderation%20filters%20our%20GPU%20inference%20research%20and%20programming%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7468374881861246976%3Fcompact%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bmythos%20will%20be%20bad%20ON%20PURPOSE%20on%20ai%20'frontier%20llm%20research'%20tasks%2C%20this%20is%20very%20very%20sad%20for%20the%20research%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Elie%20Bakouch%2C%20an%20AI%20model%20training%20expert%20at%20startup%20Prime%20Intellect%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BAlso%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20is%20on%20purpose%20not%20visible%20to%20the%20user%20is%20crazy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20just%20not%20help%20you%2C%20it%20will%20lie%20and%20purposefully%20give%20you%20bad%20info%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20AI%20developer%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20'ethical%20AI'%20company%20with%20the%20most%20brazenly%20unethical%20LLM%2C%20on%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20adds%20more%20fuel%20to%20the%20fiery%20debate%20over%20why%20Anthropic%20didn't%20immediately%20release%20Mythos%20when%20it%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmozilla-anthropic-mythos-hundreds-flaws-fuzzers-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20there%20have%20been%20three%20theories%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20official%20reason%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnthropic%20held%20Mythos%20back%20because%20it%20was%20too%20dangerous%2C%20and%20it%20needed%20to%20give%20cybersecurity%20researchers%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20new%20model.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20compute%20theory%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mythos%20is%20a%20huge%2C%20expensive%20model%20to%20run.%20Anthropic%20didn't%20have%20enough%20compute%20to%20release%20it%20fully.%20It%20has%20since%20struck%20huge%20new%20compute%20deals%2C%20which%20may%20have%20helped%20it%20release%20Fable%205%20and%20Mythos%205%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20competitive%20theory%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI%20companies%20increasingly%20worry%20about%20something%20called%20distillation.%20When%20a%20frontier%20model%20is%20released%2C%20rivals%20can%20collect%20its%20outputs%20and%20use%20that%20data%20to%20improve%20their%20own%20systems.%20Anthropic%20may%20have%20wanted%20to%20keep%20its%20best%20capabilities%20out%20of%20competitors'%20hands%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20especially%20from%20open-source%20rivals%20and%20fast-moving%20Chinese%20AI%20labs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20Anthropic%20has%20baked%20these%20AI%20research%20limitations%20into%20its%20official%20Mythos%20launch%2C%20this%20third%20theory%20is%20looking%20a%20lot%20more%20believable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-furious-anthropic-mythos-fable-hidden-ai-limits-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781052406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28abf0b19390180e4ced1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-furious-anthropic-mythos-fable-hidden-ai-limits-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20faces%20backlash%20as%20Mythos-based%20models%20intentionally%20limit%20help%20for%20AI