December_19.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1280%2Cheight%3D720%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fgurgaon-news%2Fgurugram-man-held-hostage-over-old-dispute-4-friends-arrested-cops-11614852%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20victim%20was%20rescued%20by%20police%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20the%20four%20accused%20were%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20after%20being%20produced%20in%20a%20city%20court%2C%20they%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fgurgaon-news%2Fgurugram-man-held-hostage-over-old-dispute-4-friends-arrested-cops-11614852%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fgurgaon-news%2Fgurugram-man-held-hostage-over-old-dispute-4-friends-arrested-cops-11614852%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fgurgaon-news%2Fgurugram-man-held-hostage-over-old-dispute-4-friends-arrested-cops-11614852%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20FDA%20just%20glowed%20up%20your%20sunscreen%20%E2%80%94%20by%20approving%20a%20popular%20ingredient%20in%20European%20and%20Asian%20formulas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20putting%20on%20sunscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28998d59f798e5451f5516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20new%20FDA-approved%20ingredient%20can%20make%20US%20sunscreens%20more%20efficient%20and%20luxurious-feeling.%3Cp%3ELordHenriVoton%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FDA%20just%20approved%20bemotrizinol%20(BEMT)%2C%20a%20popular%20ingredient%20in%20European%20and%20Asian%20sunscreens.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20FDA%20approved%20a%20new%20sunscreen%20ingredient%20since%201999.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20decades%2C%20US%20sunscreen%20lagged%20behind%20other%20countries'%20in%20effectiveness%20and%20smoothness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20haul%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-sunscreen-moisturizer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFrench%20sunscreens%3C%2Fa%3E%20home%20from%20your%20vacation%20%E2%80%94%20or%20pay%20exorbitant%20shipping%20fees%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20your%20hands%20on%20the%20good%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20just%20approved%20bemotrizinol%20(BEMT)%2C%20an%20ingredient%20used%20in%20European%20and%20Asian%20sunscreens%20for%20over%2020%20years.%20It's%20the%20first%20upgrade%20to%20US%20sunscreen%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBEMT%20is%20a%20chemical%20UV%20filter%20that%20absorbs%20both%20UVA%20and%20UVB%20rays%2C%20and%20doesn't%20break%20down%20easily%20when%20exposed%20to%20sunlight%2C%20making%20it%20more%20effective%20at%20protecting%20against%20skin%20cancer%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskincare-habits-that-lead-to-faster-wrinkles-aging-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epreventing%20wrinkles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20regulatory%20differences%2C%20the%20US's%20sunscreen%20formulas%20have%20remained%20notoriously%20old-fashioned%2C%20lagging%20behind%20other%20countries%20like%20the%20UK%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20which%20have%20been%20proactive%20in%20approving%20new%2C%20advanced%20UV-blocking%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20sunscreens%20sold%20in%20these%20countries%20offer%20better%20protection%20against%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sunscreen-is-not-enough-to-protect-you-from-sun-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUVA%20and%20UVB%20rays%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20also%20providing%20smoother%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20about%20to%20change%20%E2%80%94%20but%20consumers%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20over%20a%20year%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20these%20new%20and%20improved%20American%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b26ac37-13f8-4d3b-8217-d3002cb6aa27%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20biggest%20FDA%20filter%20update%20since%201999%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20applying%20sunscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a289dbca74097c573988816%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20taken%20decades%20to%20approve%20new%20sunscreen%20ingredients%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EDrazen%20Zigic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20treats%20sunscreens%20as%20non-prescription%20drugs%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20each%20ingredient%20has%20to%20go%20through%20a%20lengthy%20regulatory%20approval%20process.%20While%20this%20sounds%20good%20in%20theory%2C%20it's%20led%20to%20slow-moving%20sunscreen%20advancement%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-is-lobbying-for-looser-us-sunscreen-regulations-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20FDA%20hasn't%20approved%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20new%20UV-blocking%20filter%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20US%20sunscreens%20are%20completely%20ineffective.%20According%20to%20Dr.%20Ellen%20Gendler%2C%20a%20dermatologist%20practicing%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20US%20sunscreens%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%26quot%3B%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-wear-sunscreen-on-a-flight-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblocking%20UVB%20rays%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ones%20that%20cause%20sunburn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20said%20we%20only%20have%20only%20one%20ingredient%20approved%20for%20UVA%20blockage%3A%20Avobenzone%2C%20which%20she%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bnot%20very%20stable%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20need%20of%20other%20ingredients%20to%20make%20it%20effective.%20UVA%20rays%20are%20deeper-penetrating%2C%20which%20is%20why%20you%20can%20still%20get%20a%20tan%20while%20wearing%20US%20sunscreen%20%E2%80%94%20something%20Gendler%20noted%20might%20be%20%26quot%3Beven%20more%20harmful%20to%20the%20skin%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20damage%20done%20by%20UVB%20rays%2C%20because%20UVA%20rays%20are%20known%20to%20cause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F21-year-old-skin-cancer-melanoma-doctors-missed-symptoms-mole-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskin%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESPF%20also%20isn't%20an%20indicator%20of%20protection%20against%20UVA.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20patients%20use%20Neutrogena%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20they%20say%2C%20'I'm%20using%20an%20SPF%2070'%2C%20and%20they're%20still%20tan%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20because%20they're%20not%20well%20protected%20against%20ultraviolet%20A.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228fdc7dd1-b2a9-4051-84ae-6ca33f691380%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20search%20for%20a%20sleeker%20formula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20applying%20sunscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a289deea74097c573988818%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20common%20complaint%20of%20US%20sunscreens%20is%20that%20they%20leave%20a%20white%20cast.%3Cp%3EMeeko%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20the%20US%2C%20sunscreens%20in%20other%20countries%20are%20classified%20as%20cosmetics%20and%20not%20non-prescription%20drugs%2C%20making%20them%20subject%20to%20more%20lax%20regulations%20and%20faster%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20being%20more%20effective%20at%20protecting%20the%20skin%2C%20they%20also%20cause%20less%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-sunscreen-for-dark-skin-tones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhite%20cast%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20feel%20less%20greasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGendler%20advises%20her%20patients%20to%20layer%20chemical%20and%20mineral%20sunscreens%20with%20zinc%20oxide%20for%20better%20protection%20%E2%80%94%20but%20even%20that%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20afford%20them%20the%20same%20broad%20spectrum%20as%20the%20European%20products%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20her%20favorite%20international%20sunscreen%20is%20La%20Roche%20Posay's%20SPF%2050%20Anthelios%20UVMune%20400%20sunscreen%2C%20which%20comes%20in%20multiple%20formulas%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Binvisible%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btinted.%26quot%3B%20It%20uses%20Mexoryl%20400%2C%20an%20advanced%20version%20of%20Mexoryl%2C%20which%20has%20been%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fuv-index-scale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUVA-blocking%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20FDA%20has%20only%20approved%20some%20forms%20of%20Mexoryl%20in%20limited%20formulas.%20That%20means%20La%20Roche%20Posay's%20US%20versions%20of%20the%20same%20sunscreen%20don't%20include%20Mexoryl.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20only%20La%20Roche%20Posay%20product%20with%20Mexoryl%20is%20an%20SPF-15%20moisturizer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b179528-89e2-4797-98bf-686bc138cfb4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBemotrizinol%20can%20make%20for%20stronger%2C%20smoother%20sunscreens%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20putting%20sunscreen%20on%20hands%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a289e2e59f798e5451f552c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20sunscreens%20may%20start%20to%20resemble%20those%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia.%3Cp%3Emihailomilovanovic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20offering%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-sunscreen-sticks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUV%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20some%20other%20sunscreen%20ingredients%2C%20bemotrizinol%20is%20also%20supposed%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20more%20seamless%2C%20streak-free%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it'll%20take%20a%20while%20for%20new%20sunscreen%20formulas%20to%20include%20the%20ingredient.%20DSM%20Nutritional%20Products%2C%20which%20filed%20for%20FDA%20approval%20of%20bemotrizinol%20as%20a%20sunscreen%20ingredient%20in%202024%2C%20will%20have%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20sell%20their%20proprietary%20BEMT%20formulation%20in%20the%20US%20for%2018%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fhealth%2F491334%2Fnew-sunscreen-ingredient-bemt-bemotrizinol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Vox%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20that%2C%20other%20cosmetic%20companies%20will%20likely%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftravel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evacation%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20coming%20up%2C%20you%20can%20always%20leave%20some%20extra%20room%20in%20your%20luggage%20on%20your%20way%20back%20home.%20Or%2C%20you%20can%20always%20call%20in%20a%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20friends%20are%20going%20to%20Europe%2C%20instead%20of%20bringing%20you%20back%20a%20scarf%2C%20tell%20them%20to%20bring%20you%20back%20sunscreen%2C%26quot%3B%20Gendler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-approved-first-new-sunscreen-ingredient-in-decades-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781048120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a289ac8b19390180e4cece7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-approved-first-new-sunscreen-ingredient-in-decades-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20decades%2C%20US%20sunscreens