t%20amounts%20of%20capital%2C%20both%20are%20racing%20to%20get%20to%20market%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20to%20beat%20one%20another%20out%20due%20to%20the%20significant%20amount%20of%20capital%20both%20firms%20are%20looking%20to%20raise%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20said%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20face%20competitive%20pressures%20from%20competitors%20like%20Anthropic%20to%20show%20that%20growth%20continues%20to%20accelerate%20and%20will%20maintain%20its%20current%20aggressive%20pace%20through%20the%20next%20decade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b556dfa7-3b8c-4967-a473-62e28c5eb5ac%5C%22%3EDan%20Niles%2C%20founder%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Niles%20Investment%20Management%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Niles%20said%20he%20views%20Anthropic%20more%20favorably%20than%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Google%20wins%20in%20consumer%2C%20they%20have%20the%20complete%20stack%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20told%20CNBC.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20win%20in%20AI%20overall%2C%20but%20then%20in%20corporate%2C%20you%20have%20Anthropic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENiles%20said%20that%20Anthropic%20reached%20profitability%20in%20Q2%20%26quot%3Band%20their%20revenues%20are%20ramping%20like%20nothing%20you've%20ever%20seen%20in%20history%20for%20a%20company%20of%20that%20size.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20OpenAI%20is%20stuck%20between%20the%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20for%20me%2C%20those%20are%20the%20two%20winners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221901aec2-1613-438a-b304-e8b4b3a40ca8%5C%22%3EMichael%20Fertik%2C%20founder%20of%20Verdict%20Capital%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221713%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Fertik%20speaks%20during%20an%20event%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a284956ea70485acd8b233c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221285%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Fertik%2C%20founder%20of%20Verdict%20Capital%3Cp%3EChris%20J.%20Ratcliffe%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Fertik%2C%20founder%20of%20Verdict%20Capital%2C%20said%20he%20hopes%20SpaceX's%20IPO%20on%20Friday%20opens%20the%20door%20%26quot%3Bto%20a%20gushing%20torrent%20of%20liquidity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20rooting%20for%20Elon%20Musk.%20I'm%20rooting%20for%20the%20IPOs.%20I'm%20rooting%20for%20the%20OpenAIs%20and%20Anthropics%2C%26quot%3B%20Fertik%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFertik%20said%20that%20companies%20debuting%20strongly%20would%20help%20the%20US%20stay%20ahead%20in%20the%20generative%20AI%20race.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20many%20companies%20have%20been%20relying%20on%20private%20markets%20for%20so%20long%20that%20it's%20time%20for%20retail%20investors%20to%20share%20in%20the%20AI%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20it%20does%20encourage%20companies%20that%20have%20been%20getting%20ready%20to%20file%2C%20to%20file%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20SpaceX's%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e70fe340-e8bf-4bff-9d14-67e80a07605b%5C%22%3EGregory%20Allen%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Decision%20Tree%20Research%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGregory%20Allen%2C%20CEO%20of%20Decision%20Tree%20Research%2C%20said%20OpenAI's%20valuations%2C%20along%20with%20those%20of%20SpaceX%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20are%20really%20extraordinary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20companies%20are%20in%20the%20ballpark%20of%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20valuation%2C%26quot%3B%20Allen%20told%20CNBC%2C%20adding%20that%20in%20annuity%20terms%2C%20that%20is%20akin%20to%20%26quot%3Ban%20annuity%20that%20kicks%20out%20%2445%20billion%20a%20year%20every%20year%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%20said%20even%20though%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20are%20going%20to%20lose%20money%20this%20year%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20gross%20margins%20in%20these%20businesses%20are%20extremely%20favorable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%2C%20can%20they%20time%20the%20investments%20correctly%2C%20to%20make%20these%2C%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20capital%20expenditure%20investments%20and%20ride%20the%20wave%20of%20revenue%20growth%20properly%2C%20such%20that%20they%20don't%20run%20out%20of%20cash%20and%20go%20bankrupt%2C%20which%20is%20the%20big%20risk%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ae24f15-4fb3-40fe-a538-400b96bb4365%5C%22%3EGary%20Marcus%2C%20AI%20researcher%20and%20professor%20emeritus%20at%20New%20York%20University%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gary%20Marcus%20speaks%20during%20the%20Digital%20Life%20Design%20innovation%20conference%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28494a67142ea6832ce843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20researcher%20Gary%20Marcus%3Cp%3EMatthias%20Balk%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Marcus%2C%20an%20AI%20researcher%20and%20author%20known%20for%20his%20critical%20views%20of%20the%20AI%20industry%2C%20suggested%20buyers%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20where%20the%20AI%20industry%20stands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bi%20used%20to%20be%20the%20only%20person%20saying%20the%20emperor%20was%20wearing%20no%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20Marcus%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20quoting%20a%20tweet%20about%20SpaceX's%20valuation.%20%26quot%3Bthose%20days%20are%20over.%20the%20only%20people%20buying%20SpaceX%20and%20OpenAI%20at%20list%20price%20will%20be%20the%20stragglers%20who%20still%20can't%20see%20it.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200f2dfb1-9f4a-4a99-be84-538180e4132c%5C%22%3ENate%20Elliott%2C%20principal%20analyst%20at%20EMARKETER%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221041%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nate%20Elliot%20of%20EMARKETER%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a284940208d75cc7b7926f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENate%20Elliot%20of%20EMARKETER%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20EMARKETER%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20%26quot%3Bis%20filing%20to%20go%20public%20at%20a%20precarious%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nate%20Elliott%2C%20a%20principal%20analyst%20at%20EMARKETER%2C%20a%20sister%20company%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20is%20just%20about%20to%20lose%20its%20strong%20early%20leads%20in%20both%20consumer%20and%20enterprise%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Elliott%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnthropic%20has%20generated%20incredible%20momentum%20in%20the%20enterprise%20market%2C%20and%20EMARKETER%20forecasts%20that%20Google%20will%20overtake%20ChatGPT%20in%20terms%20of%20US%20AI%20users%20by%20early%202027.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElliott%20said%20OpenAI%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20places%20to%20look%20for%20the%20enormous%20capital%20required%20to%20support%20its%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20has%20taken%20almost%20%24200%20billion%20in%20funding%20across%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20private%20rounds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20can't%20count%20on%20its%20consumer%20business%20becoming%20self-sufficient%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4cffbbb-2993-459b-a62e-f7eb76fa778a%5C%22%3EJoshua%20Achiam%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20futurist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20full%20OpenAI%20news%20cycle%20without%20someone%20taking%20a%20shot%20at%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Achiam%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20futurist%2C%20framed%20the%20discussion%20as%20a%20choice%20between%20two%20very%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-dario-amodei-anthropic-openai-rivalry-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edifferent%20goals%20of%20the%20now%20rival%20companies.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20a%20loving%20ensouled%20machine%20God%20watch%20over%20humanity%3F%20Vote%20Anthropic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BShould%20humanity%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20tools%20of%20its%20own%20progress%20and%20destiny%3F%20Vote%20OpenAI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAchiam%20dismissed%20the%20analysis%20that%20focuses%20on%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20leading%20AI%20companies'%20business%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20lens%20for%20analyzing%20this%20is%20'consumer%20v%20enterprise%20business'%20your%20ability%20to%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%20is%20unfixably%20borked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ipo-reactions-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781044809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a284377208d75cc7b7920c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ipo-reactions-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Financial%20analysts%2C%20CEOs%2C%20and%20researchers%20dissect%20how%20OpenAI%20is%20positioned%20as%20it%20enters%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20the%20AI%20race%3A%20preparing%20to%20go%20public.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eva%20reveals%20painful%20details%20of%20marriage%20to%20Aamir%E2%80%99s%20stepbrother%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781044807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131622067%2Cimgsize-75278.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Feva-grover-reveals-painful-details-of-marriage-to-aamir-khans-stepbrother-hyder-ali-khan-having-a-child-doesnt-fix-a-broken-marriage%2Farticleshow%