3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Air%20India%20asking%20kin%20of%20crash%20victims%20to%20waive%20claims%20before%20facts%20known%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781041248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131620250%2Cimgsize-132654.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fair-india-asking-kin-of-crash-victims-to-waive-claims-before-facts-known%2Farticleshow%2F131620102.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Airline%20refutes%20charge%20by%20former%20Gujarat%20CM%E2%80%99s%20daughter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAURABH%20SINHA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GM%20wants%20your%20EV%20to%20help%20power%20the%20grid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222481%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20electric%20car%20plugged%20into%20a%20home%20charging%20system.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2764140421ca48aa59fff1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221241%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGM%20said%20it%20has%20250%2C000%20EVs%20on%20US%20roads%20that%20could%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20energy%20source%20for%20power%20grids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20General%20Motors%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20data%20center%20buildout%20is%20driving%20a%20historic%20surge%20in%20electricity%20demand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGeneral%20Motors%20proposes%20leveraging%20personal%20EVs%20to%20help%20balance%20the%20power%20grid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20GM%20executive%20told%20Business%20Insider%20this%20program%20could%20result%20in%20lower%20utility%20bills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-interview-ai-prototypes-design-cars-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Motors%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20use%20the%20parked%20EV%20in%20your%20garage%20to%20power%20the%20energy%20grid%20and%20potentially%20lower%20your%20utility%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legacy%20automaker%20is%20pitching%20EV%20batteries%20as%20a%20power%20source%20that%20could%20help%20utility%20companies%20manage%20surging%20electricity%20demand%2C%20as%20households%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bills-surge-utilities-31b-rate-increases-2025-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erate%20increases%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20US%20sees%20historic%20levels%20of%20energy%20consumption%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-near-me-location-tracker-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20build-out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20utility%20executives%20and%20energy%20lawmakers%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20GM%20called%20on%20utility%20agencies%2C%20regulators%2C%20and%20automakers%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bpublic-private%20collaboration%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20EV%20drivers%20to%20send%20power%20back%20to%20the%20grid.%20Stakeholders%20would%20work%20out%20logistics%20like%20customer%20enrollment%2C%20incentives%2C%20and%20rate%20structures%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20growth%20and%20consumption%20of%20electricity%20in%20the%20US%20has%20been%20at%20historic%20highs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurt%20Kelty%2C%20GM's%20vice%20president%20of%20battery%20and%20sustainability%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20never%20had%20such%20a%20high%20growth%20rate%20in%20electricity%20for%20probably%20a%20hundred%20years%20or%20so.%20That's%20partly%20being%20driven%20by%20the%20AI%20data%20center%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Energy%20Information%20Administration%20said%20in%20January%20that%20it%20expects%20electricity%20use%20to%20rise%201%25%20this%20year%20and%203%25%20in%202027%2C%20marking%20the%20strongest%20four-year%20stretch%20of%20demand%20growth%20since%202000.%20The%20agency%20said%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20from%20large%20computing%20centers%26quot%3B%20was%20behind%20the%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Business%20Insider%20analysis%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-ai-data-center-power-electricity-use-consumption-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20data%20center%20permits%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20if%20all%20facilities%20permitted%20through%202025%20came%20online%2C%20they%20could%20consume%20between%20224.3%20terawatt-hours%20and%20358.8%20terawatt-hours%20of%20electricity%20a%20year.%20At%20the%20midpoint%2C%20that's%20more%20than%20the%20total%20electricity%20use%20by%20any%20US%20state%20outside%20Texas%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ease%20grid%20demand%2C%20GM%20said%20it%20could%20leverage%20bidirectional%20charging%20technology%2C%20which%20allows%20power%20to%20flow%20into%20and%20out%20of%20the%20EV.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20has%20more%20than%20250%2C000%20bidirectional%20EVs%20on%20US%20roads%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20building%20that%20capability%20across%20its%20entire%20EV%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20million%20EVs%2C%20GM%20said%20that%20amounts%20to%20power%20for%20about%20120%2C000%20homes%20for%20up%20to%20one%20week%20or%20all%20of%20San%20Francisco%20for%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GM's%20energy%20home%20system.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2884caa74097c573988780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGM's%20energy%20home%20system%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20GM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKelty%20described%20the%20future%20customer%20experience%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20low%2C%20sell%20high%26quot%3B%20scenario%20for%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20driver%20could%20come%20home%20from%20work%2C%20plug%20in%2C%20and%20let%20the%20EV%20discharge%20power%20during%20peak%20demand%20times%2C%20such%20as%20late%20afternoon%20or%20evening.%20Then%20the%20car%20could%20recharge%20later%20at%20night%2C%20when%20electricity%20is%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelty%20added%20that%20this%20process%20wouldn't%20happen%20every%20day%20and%20that%20utility%20companies%20may%20only%20need%20the%20extra%20support%2020%20or%2030%20days%20out%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20EV%20would%20also%20not%20be%20fully%20discharged%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20much%20extra%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20the%20battery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20battery%20would%20still%20be%20covered%20under%20warranty%20as%20long%20as%20customers%20followed%20a%20GM-specific%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20customers%20will%20see%20returns%20through%20credits%2C%20lower%20utility%20bills%2C%20or%20a%20cheaper%20EV%20at%20initial%20purchase%20is%20all%20on%20the%20table%2C%20Kelty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20phases.%20GM%20said%20it's%20now%20testing%20%26quot%3Bvehicle-to-grid%26quot%3B%20programs%20with%20utility%20agencies%2C%20including%20PG%26amp%3BE%20in%20northern%20California%20and%20DTE%20Energy%20in%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20a%20similar%20concept%20with%20Powershare%2C%20which%20allows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-owner-highlights-complaints-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECybertruck%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20use%20the%20truck's%20battery%20to%20power%20a%20home%20and%2C%20in%20some%20regions%2C%20support%20the%20grid.%20However%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20currently%20only%20centered%20on%20the%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20thing%20we're%20looking%20at%20is%20we%20want%20to%20sell%20more%20EVs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelty%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20reduce%20fossil%20fuel%20consumption.%20That's%20the%20direction%20we%20want%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-general-motors-ev-battery-power-grid-ai-data-center-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781041155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2764415bcf40c28b6b0681%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-general-motors-ev-battery-power-grid-ai-data-center-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22General%20Motors%20says%20EVs%20can%20send%20power%20back%20to%20the%20grid%20and%20potentially%20lower%20household%20utility%20bills%20through%20public-private%20partnership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Late%20Late%20Show%E2%80%99%20Host%20Craig%20Ferguson%20Is%20%E2%80%98Glad%E2%80%99%20He%20Ended%20His%20Show%20Before%20Trump%20Became%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781040915000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236770899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Craig%20Ferguson%2C%20the%20former%20host%20of%20CBS%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Late%20Late%20Show%2C%E2%80%9D%20recently%20told%20%E2%80%9CObsessed%3A%20The%20Podcast%E2%80%9D%20that%20he%20was%20glad%20he%20got%20out%20of%20the%20late-night%20game%20before%20Donald%20Trump%20became%20president.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20I%20would%20have%20handled%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ferguson%20admitted.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20thought%20about%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jack%20Dunn%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IShowSpeed%20lands%20major%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%202026%20role%20after%20surprise%20trailer%20with%20Gianni%20Infantino%20goes%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22p