20Marshall%2CLillian%20Brown)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20the%20standard%20severance%20package%20Salesforce%20offers%20laid-off%20US%20employees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salesforce%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a287bd4a74097c573988738%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalesforce%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Fanjoy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESalesforce%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-cuts-jobs-agentforce-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20new%20round%20of%20cuts%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20internal%20document%20shows%20Salesforce's%20standard%20severance%20offer%20for%20U.S.%20employees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEmployees%20receive%20severance%20based%20on%20level%2C%20tenure%2C%20and%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Salesforce%20begins%20another%20round%20of%20layoffs%2C%20the%20company's%20standard%20severance%20plan%20appears%20to%20offer%20employees%20a%20softer%20landing%20than%20many%20of%20its%20Big%20Tech%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show%20that%20eligible%20U.S.%20workers%20can%20receive%20up%20to%2030%20weeks%20of%20severance%2C%20a%20package%20that%20appears%20more%20generous%20than%20those%20recently%20offered%20by%20companies%20including%20Oracle%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20on%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-cuts-jobs-agentforce-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20notifying%20employees%20about%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20and%20a%20regulatory%20notice%20in%20California.%20The%20layoffs%20come%20amid%20concerns%20that%20AI%20tools%20and%20agents%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-microsoft-stocks-down-ai-replacement-future-of-software-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereplace%20traditional%20software%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20company's%20main%20customer%20relationship-management%20offering.%20Salesforce's%20stock%20is%20down%20more%20than%2030%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce's%20severance%20policy%20states%20that%20employees%20receive%20severance%20payments%20based%20on%20level%2C%20tenure%2C%20and%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20directors%20and%20director-level%20employees%20receive%2013%20weeks%20of%20base%20pay%2C%20while%20senior%20managers%20and%20below%20receive%209%20weeks.%20Employees%20ages%2060%20and%20older%20at%20any%20level%20get%20an%20additional%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20also%20receive%20an%20additional%20three%20weeks%20of%20service%20per%20year.%20A%20partial%20year%20counts%20as%20a%20full%20year.%20Employees%20receive%20six%20months%20of%20COBRA%20coverage%2C%20or%2012%20months%20if%20they%20are%2060%20or%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20total%20of%20level-%20and%20tenure-based%20is%20capped%20at%2026%20weeks%2C%20or%2030%20weeks%20for%20those%2060%20and%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce's%20package%20appears%20larger%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-severance-package-comparison-big-tech-layoffs-2026-2%23meta-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethan%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-severance-package-comparison-big-tech-layoffs-2026-2%23meta-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20other%20recent%20Big%20Tech%20severance%20offers.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Oracle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2