20payment%20for%20Norton%20Antivirus%20identity%20theft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fbest-identity-theft-protection-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotection%20software%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20was%20not%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20from%20Norton%2C%20but%20from%20the%20scammers.%20Maas%2C%20a%20former%20human%20relations%20professional%2C%20who%20had%20not%20ordered%20the%20service%2C%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bhelpline%26quot%3B%20number%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20reached%20a%20man%2C%20who%20called%20himself%20Jason%20Green%20and%20said%20he%20was%20an%20agent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-set-up-a-paypal-account%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20PayPal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20he%20could%20refund%20the%20money%20if%20Maas%20filled%20out%20an%20online%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20provided%20details%2C%20including%20his%20bank%20name%20and%20the%20last%20four%20digits%20of%20his%20PNC%20checking%20and%20money%20accounts.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20Maas%2C%20the%20scammer%20had%20also%20taken%20control%20of%20his%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20scam%3F%20Please%20send%20details%20to%20Jane%20Ridley%20at%20%3Cstrong%3Ejridley%40insider.com%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20if%20you'd%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%20began%20the%20%26quot%3Brefund%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20told%20Maas%20he%20had%20accidentally%20deposited%20%24300%2C000%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbusiness-checking-vs-personal-checking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echecking%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Green%20used%20his%20computer%20access%20to%20show%20Maas%20a%20falsified%20PNC%20statement%20recording%20the%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c83d3c07-73c1-4c37-8735-3c2b5587facf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaas%20was%20told%20he%20could%20incur%20penalties%20from%20the%20IRS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20kept%20saying%20he%20would%20be%20fired%20if%20his%20mistake%20was%20discovered%2C%26quot%3B%20Maas%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20scammer%20was%20slick%20and%20solicitous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20scammer%2C%20to%20whom%20the%20first%20conman%20directed%20to%20call%2C%20told%20Maas%20that%20the%20only%20way%20he%20could%20refund%20the%20%24300%2C000%20without%20incurring%20financial%20penalties%20from%20the%20IRS%20was%20to%20deposit%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20day%2C%20Maas%20visited%20his%20regular%20PNC%20branch%20in%20West%20Orange%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20to%20authorize%20the%20wiring%20of%20%24300%2C000%20to%20American%20Coin%20and%20Stamp%20Co%2C%20Inc.%2C%20a%20precious-metal%20dealer%20based%20in%20Clifton%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%20scammers%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fis-gold-a-good-investment-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20scam%20are%20described%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20the%20Law%20Division%20of%20the%20Superior%20Court%20of%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Essex%20County.%20In%20it%2C%20Maas%20claims%20negligence%20against%20PNC%20and%20American%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20senior%20wearing%20a%20jacket%20that%20says%20Australia%20on%20it.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a283d0fea70485acd8b1991%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaas%20lost%20half%20of%20his%20life%20savings%20in%20the%20scam.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jeffrey%20Maas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20suing%20a%20Pennsylvanian%20named%20Jaynesh%20Patel%2C%20alleging%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20conversion%20and%20con