3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-new-jersey-west-virginia-regrets-poor-healthcare-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Jersey%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3Elicense%20plate%20arrived%2C%20and%20Maas%20placed%20the%20coins%20in%20the%20back%20seat%20through%20an%20open%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20Green%20told%20Maas%20that%20the%20process%20had%20been%20successful%20and%20offered%20him%20a%20%241%2C000%20reward%20for%20his%20help%2C%20which%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said%2C%20Maas%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293088e75-7db3-4775-a551-9bcc99e3d034%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaas%20was%20shown%20a%20forged%20document%20depicting%20his%20bank%20account%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20a%20reward%2C'%26quot%3B%20Maas%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20to%20leave%20me%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20then%20told%20Maas%20that%2C%20instead%2C%20he%20would%20pay%20Maas%20%2410%2C000%20compensation%20because%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bsaved%20his%20job.%26quot%3B%20As%20Maas%20completed%20the%20supposed%20reward%20form%2C%20Green%20said%20there%20had%20been%20another%20mistake%3A%20%24100%2C000%20had%20been%20credited%20to%20his%20account%2C%20not%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaas%20was%20again%20shown%20a%20forged%20document%20depicting%20his%20PNC%20account%20with%20the%20latest%20deposit%20and%20told%20he%20would%20need%20to%20repeat%20the%20process%20of%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Jersey%20resident%20returned%20to%20PNC%20and%20withdrew%20%2490%2C000.%20The%20suit%20alleges%20that%20Maas%20was%20on%20an%20open%20phone%20line%20and%20that%20the%20second%20banker%20who%20helped%20him%20did%20not%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20needed%20the%20funds%20for%2C%20or%20note%20that%20he%20had%20withdrawn%20the%20%24300%2C00%20the%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4eb7c0e-5c67-49b1-b184-c23ae3d38894%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaas%20requested%20that%20the%20wires%20be%20recalled%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMaas'%20complaint%20said%20the%20banker%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20alert%20Mr.%20Maas%20that%20this%20withdrawal%20would%20essentially%20wipe%20out%20the%20savings%20in%20his%20checking%20and%20money%20market%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaas%20then%20returned%20to%20Angello%20and%20purchased%20more%20coins.%20This%20time%2C%20a%20green%20Honda%20with%20Pennsylvania%20plates%20came%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20Green%2C%20but%20I%20just%20figured%20something%20wasn't%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Maas%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20After%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Flack-of-sleep-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esleepless%20night%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%26quot%3Bagitation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20humiliation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20filed%20a%20report%20with%20the%20West%20Orange%20Police%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223556%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20branch%20of%20PNC%20Bank%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a283e0467142ea6832cdec1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaas%20is%20suing%20PNC%20Bank%20and%20two%20other%20defendants.%3Cp%3EAP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOfficers%20identified%20the%20Honda%20driver%20as%20Patel%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest%20and%20indictment%20on%20a%20second-degree%20theft%20by%20deception%20charge.%20He%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%2C%20and%20his%20next%20court%20appearance%20is%20on%20July%206%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20Maas%20reported%20the%20situation%20to%20PNC%20and%20requested%20the%20wires%20be%20recalled%2C%20only%20to%20learn%20that%20it%20could%20not%20be%20done.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20hoping%20it%20was%20a%20bad%20dream%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20Maas%20said%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20two%20severe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fdizzy-spells%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepisodes%20of%20fainting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20doctors%20diagnosed%20as%20the%20result%20of%20stress.%20He%20spent%20three%20days%20in%20the%20hospital%20on%20both%20occasions%20and%20suffered%20from%20severe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fsocial-anxiety-disorder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3Eand%20avoidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22098cd355-582e-4819-9b66-fe8c0dc20ddc%5C%22%3EThe%20coin%20dealer%20has%20denied%20all%20wrongdoing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20neither%20the%20bank%20nor%20the%20dealer%20took%20the%20necessary%20precautions%20to%20prevent%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-couple-ftc-scam-retirement-fund-bitcoin-gold-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelaborate%20con%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20PNC%20and%20Patel's%20attorneys%20in%20both%20the%20civil%20and%20criminal%20cases%20against%20him.%20PNC%2C%20which%20has%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%20on%20legal%20grounds%2C%20said%20it%20could%20not%20comment%20on%20active%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel's%20attorneys%20have%20not%20responded%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request.%20However%2C%20in%20his%20answer%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20Patel%20denied%20Maas'%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Angello%2C%20owner%20of%20American%20Coin%2C%20denied%20wrongdoing.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20%26quot%3Babsurd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20livid%20that%20they%20are%20taking%20shots%20at%20my%20company%20and%20me%20when%20we've%20been%20here%20for%2070%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20name%20is%20being%20sullied.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20case%20was%20keeping%20him%20up%20at%20night%2C%20and%20he%20was%20considering%20counter-suing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf7b4d34-83cf-4b44-90ba-dd07b2bd618e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaas%20wants%20to%20raise%20awareness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Maas%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20my%20wife%20yelled%20at%20me%2C%20but%20she%20and%20my%20family%20have%20been%20super%20about%20what%20happened%2C%20but%20I'm%20my%20own%20worst%20enemy.%20Nobody%20held%20a%20gun%20to%20my%20head%2C%20but%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22753%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20outstretched%20palm%20of%20gold%20coins.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a283f32208d75cc7b791d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22565%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaas%20bought%20gold%20coins%20and%20lost%20a%20total%20%24390K%3Cp%3EMohamed%20Abd%20El%20Ghany%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20was%20left%20shaken%2C%20and%20his%20regret%20at%20what%20happened%20wouldn't%20go%20away.%20As%20for%20his%20attitude%20toward%20PNC%2C%20American%20Coin%2C%20and%20Patel%2C%20Maas%20said%20he%20wanted%20nothing%20more%20to%20do%20with%20them%2C%20but%20hopes%20to%20recover%20damages%2C%20attorney's%20fees%2C%20and%20court%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaas'%20attorney%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pollockcohen.com%2Fteam%2Fsteve-cohen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteve%20Cohen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20said%20scams%20against%20older%20Americans%20are%20prolific%2C%20accused%20financial%20entities%20such%20as%20PNC%20and%20American%20Coin%20of%20being%20as%20crucial%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20con%20as%20the%20frontline%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20ignored%20all%20the%20red%20flags%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BJeffrey%20has%20been