ts%20while%20they%20learn%20and%20then%20guarantees%20a%20job%20for%20all%20graduates%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20said.%20It%20will%20initially%20launch%20in%20Louisiana%2C%20Ohio%2C%20Indiana%2C%20and%20Texas%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20prior%20experience%20is%20required%2C%20and%20Meta%20said%20every%20graduate%20will%20leave%20with%20a%20verified%2C%20industry-standard%20credential%20in%20fields%20such%20as%20electrical%20work%2C%20mechanical%20systems%2C%20and%20plumbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20Meta%20announced%20in%20April%20a%20four-week%20training%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-fast-track-fiber-technician-training-fix-data-center-bottleneck-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogram%20for%20new%20fiber%20technicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20to%20begin%20this%20summer.%20Meta%20said%20that%20initiative%2C%20called%20Level-Up%2C%20received%2035%2C000%20applications%20in%20the%20first%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20new%20workforce%20initiatives%20show%20the%20AI%20boom%20is%20creating%20a%20scramble%20for%20people%20who%20can%20build%20and%20operate%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20behind%20the%20technology.%20Even%20as%20tech%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrim%20their%20white-collar%20workforces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20are%20increasingly%20competing%20for%20electricians%2C%20fiber%20technicians%2C%20and%20other%20skilled%20tradespeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20all%20the%20rhetoric%20about%20automation%2C%20AI%20still%20depends%20on%20a%20massive%20human%20workforce%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Kaufman%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20e-commerce%20giant%20StockX%20and%20a%20leadership%20consultant.%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%20may%20be%20more%20automated%2C%20but%20somebody%20still%20has%20to%20build%20the%20data%20centers%2C%20run%20the%20fiber%2C%20and%20keep%20the%20lights%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ba4c468-3864-40f4-b8a6-9489e65718bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20demand%20for%20hard%20hats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20permits%20were%20issued%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-ai-data-center-power-electricity-use-consumption-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E176%20new%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%2034%20states%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20new%20permits%20in%20one%20year%20since%20the%20first%20was%20issued%20in%201976%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20construction%20industry%20needs%20an%20estimated%20349%2C000%20new%20workers%20this%20year%20to%20meet%20demand%2C%20according%20to%20Associated%20Builders%20and%20Contractors%2C%20a%20trade%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20Americans%20face%20a%20Catch-22%2C%20they%20need%20training%20to%20get%20a%20new%20higher%20paying%20job%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20go%20without%20pay%20to%20attend%20a%20training%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Gina%20Raimondo%2C%20former%20US%20Secretary%20of%20Commerce%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fginaraimondo%2Fstatus%2F2064140707342758251%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meta's%20new%20workforce%20academy%20%26quot%3Baims%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%20with%20paid%20apprenticeships%20and%20credentials%20that%20lead%20to%20actual%2C%20available%20good%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20AI-hungry%20employers'%20most-wanted%20lists%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemand-for-physical-security-workers-at-data-centers-is-growing-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20who%20can%20safeguard%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20centers.%20Job%20postings%20that%20mention%20%26quot%3Bphysical%20security%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdata%20centers%26quot%3B%20have%20nearly%20quadrupled%20since%20early%202020%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20long%20these%20new%20data%20center%20jobs%20Meta%20is%20looking%20to%20fill%20will%20last.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-tax-subsidies-jobs-ohio-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EData%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20generally%20do%20not%20create%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-utah-data-center-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20numbers%20of%20permanent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20full-time%20jobs%20in%20local%20economies%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20Researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California's%20Marshall%20School%20of%20Business%20found%20that%20once%20a%20large%20data%20center%20is%20completed%20and%20up%20and%20running%2C%20its%20on-site%20workforce%20drops%20by%20an%20average%20of%2078%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoff-meta-severance-details-cobra-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20laid%20off%20roughly%2010%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%2078%2C000%20employees%2C%20citing%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20effort%20to%20run%20the%20company%20more%20efficiently%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20help%20it%20offset%20its%20other%20investments.%20Meta%20is%20pouring%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20its%20AI%20ambitions%20and%20weaving%20the%20technology%20throughout%20its%20apps%2C%20including%20WhatsApp%2C%20Messenger%2C%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20also%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20its%20own%20employees'%20AI%20usage.%20The%20company%20installed%20new%20software%20in%20April%20on%20its%20US%20workers'%20computers%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-new-ai-tool-tracks-staff-activity-sparks-concern-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etracks%20their%20keystrokes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mouse%20movements%20to%20train%20its%20AI.%20The%20move%20sparked%20internal%20backlash%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-launches-construction-data-center-jobs-program-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781029474000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28423067142ea6832cdef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-launches-construction-data-center-jobs-program-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20tech%20giant's%20latest%20hiring%20push%20highlights%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20workers%20who%20can%20build%20AI's%20backbone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sneedleman%40businessinsider.com%20(Sarah%20E.%20Needleman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20visited%20Scotland%20with%20friends.%20Our%20trip%20would've%20been%20better%20if%20we%20had%20done%20these%205%20things%20differently.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20girls%20hugging%20at%20Dean's%20Village%20in%20Edinburgh.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690ba15c0be9845f2dc5cbcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222484%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20found%20some%20helpful%20tips%20for%20traveling%20with%20a%20group.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20went%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-know-before-visiting-scotland-first-time-mistakes%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Scotland%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20friends%2C%20and%20we%20made%20a%20few%20mistakes%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20should've%20tracked%20expenses%20during%20the%20trip%20instead%20of%20sorting%20our%20bank%20statements%20afterward.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20would've%20been%20smart%20to%20communicate%20what%20we%20were%20packing%20to%20avoid%20showing%20up%20with%20the%20same%20items.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20really%20learn%20a%20lot%20about%20people%20when%20you%20travel%20with%20them.%20A%20trip%20can%20bring%20out%20the%20best%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20most%20chaotic%20%E2%80%94%20sides%20of%20everyone%20involved%2C%20so%20if%20it's%20not%20planned%20right%2C%20things%20can%20go%20off%20the%20rails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20reminded%20of%20this%20recently%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Scotland%20with%20friends%2C%20where%20I%20realized%20that%20so%20much%20of%20the%20experience%20starts%20long%20before%20the%20plane%20takes%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20planning%20and%20packing%20to%20navigating%20new%20cities%20and%20making%20group%20decisions%2C%20every%20step%20of%20the%20journey%20takes%20patience%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20good%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20despite%20the%20stress%2C%20traveling%20together%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20ways%20to%20bond.%20When%20it's%20done%20right%2C%20those%20shared%20challenges%20and%20spontaneous%20moments%20can%20create%20memories%20that%20last%20a%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20things%20I%20would've%20done%20differently%20on%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-travel-with-friends-without-losing-friendships-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20with%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlanning%20out%20logistics%20beforehand%20would've%20made%20everything%20run%20smoothly.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223116%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Edinburgh%20Castle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e4f4c513c94655a3ddcd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222337%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20the%20planning%20process%2C%20we%20started%20a%20shared%20PowerPoint%20to%20outline%20an%20itinerary%20and%20list%20everyone's%20interests.%20However%2C%20we%20didn't%20consistently%20update%20it%2C%20so%20by%20the%20time%20we%20left%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20partial%20list%20without%20details%20or%20scheduling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20decisions%20were%20made%20on%20the%20spot%20%E2%80%94%20calling%20places%20from%20our%20Airbnb%20to%20make%20reservations%20or%20scrambling%20to%20buy%20tickets%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-scotland-castles-to-visit-and-skip-from-local-edinburgh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEdinburgh%20Castle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20were%20sold%20out%20for%20two%20days%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'd%20use%20a%20shared%20document%20or%20spreadsheet%20to%20list%20everyone's%20top%20three%20priorities%2C%20then%20map%20out%20out%20logistics%20and%20secure%20reservations%20and%20tickets%20to%20any%20must-see%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wish%20we%20had%20talked%20about%20a%20budget%20and%20set%20expectations%20early.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222419%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20girls%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%20chatting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e509c21c3f142ebfc58b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221814%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20with%20others%20means%20navigating%20different%20budgets%2C%20interests%2C%20and%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20may%20prefer%20spending%20money%20on%20rideshares%20for%20convenience%2C%20while%20others%20may%20want%20to%20splurge%20on%20fancy%20dinners%20or%20souvenirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20trip%2C%20it%20wasn't%20that%20we%20didn't%20discuss%20this%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20that%20we%20only%20did%20it%20once%20we%20got%20to%20Scotland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%