ment%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22L.A.%20Dodgers%20Star%20Shohei%20Ohtani%20Is%20Building%20Bridges%20for%20Brands%20and%20Fans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781028900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236765119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shohei%20Ohtani%20has%20broken%20records%20in%20baseball%20with%20his%20versatility%20as%20a%20power%20hitter%20and%20as%20a%20pitcher.%20The%20Japanese%20superstar%20has%20helped%20take%20the%20Dodgers%20to%20back-to-back%20World%20Series%20championships%20since%20joining%20the%20Boys%20in%20Blue%20in%202024.%20Whether%20one%20follows%20baseball%20or%20not%2C%20the%20likelihood%20is%20that%20people%20know%20or%20have%20heard%20the%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jazztangcay%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic%20releases%20Claude%20Fable%205%2C%20a%20'Mythos-class'%20AI%20model%20with%20safeguards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223761%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20laptop%20with%20Claude%20Code%20AI%20stickers.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19dd1cb4fb977f35981e49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222509%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic's%20initial%20Mythos%20AI%20model%2C%20and%20its%20ramifications%20for%20cybersecurity%2C%20drew%20major%20attention%20from%20companies%20and%20governments%20around%20the%20world.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20released%20Fable%205%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BMythos-class%26quot%3B%20model%20with%20safeguards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20previously%20held%20off%20on%20publicly%20releasing%20its%20first%20Mythos%20model%2C%20warning%20the%20AI%20was%20too%20skilled%20at%20hacking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFable%205's%20capabilities%20%26quot%3Bexceed%20those%20of%20any%20model%20we've%20ever%20made%20generally%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says%2C%20even%20with%20safeguards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ipo-filing-wall-street-analysts-investors-reactions-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20finally%20willing%20to%20give%20you%20Mythos%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20with%20some%20safeguard%20strings%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20was%20releasing%20a%20%26quot%3BMythos-class%26quot%3B%20model%20called%20Claude%20Fable%205%2C%20but%20with%20safeguards%20so%20significant%20that%20it%20gave%20the%20model%20a%20different%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20safeguards%2C%20Fable%205's%20capabilities%20in%20areas%20like%20cybersecurity%20could%20be%20misused%20to%20cause%20serious%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20said%20in%20its%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safeguards%2C%20which%20mean%20some%20queries%20on%20certain%20topics%20will%20instead%20be%20ported%20to%20Anthropic's%20Opus%204.8%20model%2C%20are%20initially%20tuned%20to%20be%20more%20conservative.%20The%20safeguards%20are%20triggered%20when%20Fable%205%20detects%20requests%20concerning%20cybersecurity%2C%20biology%20and%20chemistry%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-deepseek-distillation-minimax-moonshot-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edistillation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20users%20will%20be%20informed%20that%20their%20request%20is%20being%20routed%20through%20Opus%204.8.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFable%205%20is%20available%20immediately%20to%20all%20Pro%20and%20Max%20subscribers%20as%20well%20as%20team%20and%20enterprise%20plans%2C%20Anthropic%20said.%20That%20broad%20access%20won't%20last%20for%20long.%20Starting%20June%2023%2C%20Fable%205%20will%20require%20usage%20credits%2C%20though%20the%20company%20said%20it%20may%20extend%20the%20initial%20access%20period%20if%20there's%20sufficient%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rollout%20is%20a%20little%20clunky%20(wanted%20to%20get%20it%20into%20as%20many%20hands%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible!)%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic's%20Sam%20McAllister%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20broad%20access%20will%20likely%20be%20removed%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe'll%20be%20working%20hard%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20can%2C%20as%20more%20compute%20comes%20online.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20is%20also%20continuing%20Project%20Glasswing%2C%20which%20it%20first%20announced%20in%20April%2C%20that%20gave%20early%20access%20to%20the%20first%20version%20of%20Mythos%2C%20Claude%20Mythos%20Preview%2C%20to%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20tech%2C%20cybersecurity%2C%20and%20financial%20companies.%20The%20AI%20company%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20small%20group%20of%20cyberdefenders%20and%20infrastructure%20providers%26quot%3B%20will%20get%20access%20to%20Claude%20Mythos%205%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20model%20as%20Fable%205%20%26quot%3Bbut%20with%20the%20safeguards%20lifted%20in%20some%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20the%20strongest%20cybersecurity%20capabilities%20of%20any%20model%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20of%20Mythos%205.%20%26quot%3BSoon%2C%20we%20intend%20to%20expand%20access%20to%20Mythos%205%20through%20a%20broader%20trusted%20access%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20constraints%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20Fable%205%20%26quot%3Bexceed%20those%20of%20any%20model%20we've%20ever%20made%20generally%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20state-of-the-art%20on%20nearly%20all%20tested%20benchmarks%20of%20AI%20capability%2C%20showing%20exceptional%20performance%20in%20software%20engineering%2C%20knowledge%20work%2C%20vision%2C%20scientific%20research%2C%20and%20many%20other%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20and%20more%20complex%20the%20task%2C%20the%20larger%20Fable%205's%20lead%20over%20our%20other%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20said%20Stripe%20found%20that%20Fable%205%20compressed%20months%20of%20engineering%20into%20days.%20For%20financial%20tasks%2C%20the%20company%20said%20IMC%20found%20that%20Fable%205%20%26quot%3Baced%20their%20trading-analysis%20evaluations%20nearly%20across%20the%20board%2C%20including%20factual%20lookup%2C%20conceptual%20reasoning%2C%20root-cause%20analysis%2C%20and%20expected-value%20analysis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20previous%20Anthropic%20models%2C%20Fable%20fits%20within%20the%20theme%20of%20naming%20AI%20models%20after%20forms%20of%20composition.%20The%20AI%20startup%20said%20Fable%20was%20chosen%20because%20it%20shares%20similarities%20with%20Mythos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFable%20is%20from%20the%20Latin%20fabula%2C%20'that%20which%20is%20told%2C'%20akin%20to%20the%20Greek%20mythos%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20comes%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-pause-reactions-response-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecritical%20time%20for%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20recently%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20confidentially%20filed%20a%20draft%20S-1%2C%20officially%20kicking%20off%20the%20march%20toward%20a%20blockbuster%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20Anthropic's%20chief%20rival%2C%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20too%20had%20confidentially%20filed%20its%20S-1.%20SpaceX%2C%20which%20includes%20Elon%20Musk's%20xAI%2C%20is%20set%20to%20go%20public%20on%20Friday%20when%20it%20begins%20trading%20on%20the%20Nasdaq.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20initial%20announcement%20of%20Mythos%20spooked%20financial%20markets%20and%20governments%20worldwide%2C%20raising%20concerns%20that%20AI%20models%20had%20advanced%20to%20the%20point%20where%20they%20could%20now%20uncover%20major%20vulnerabilities%20in%20software%20and%20cybersecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20allows%20AI%20companies%20to%20voluntarily%20give%20the%20federal%20government%20access%20to%20frontier%20AI%20models%20up%20to%2030%20days%20before%20their%20release.%20The%20order%20explicitly%20prohibits%20the%20government%20from%20imposing%20a%20mandatory%20review%20on%20AI%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-fable-5-mythos-class-model-release-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781028798000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a282373ea70485acd8b17c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-fable-5-mythos-class-model-release-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20said%20it%20could%20not%20yet%20release%20the%20full%20Claude%20Mythos%205%20model%2C%20so%20instead%20it%20created%20Fable%205%20with%20baked%20in%20safeguards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic%20Opens%20Up%20Its%20Most%20Powerful%20AI%20Model%20To%20All%2C%20But%20There's%20A%20Catch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Anthropic%20has%20so%20far%20limited%20its%20access%20to%20a%20group%20of%20about%20200%20organisations%20including%20the%20US%20government%20under%20the%20Glasswing%20program%2C%20after%20announcing%20in%20April%20that%20Mythos%20had%20uncovered%20thousands%20of%20software%20vulnerabilities.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781028705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fanthropic-opens-up-its-most-powerful-ai