's%20most%20practical%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20flashy%20%E2%80%94%20AI-powered%20updates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20new%20AI%20wants%20to%20fix%20your%20bad%20passwords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-smart-people-are-saying-about-apple-ai-announcements-wwdc-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWorldwide%20Developers%20Conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20Apple%20said%20its%20Passwords%20app%20will%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20update%20eligible%20weak%20or%20compromised%20passwords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20you%20can%20automatically%20update%20eligible%20accounts%20to%20strong%20passwords%20with%20just%20a%20tap%2C%26quot%3B%20Beth%20Dakin%2C%20a%20senior%20manager%20on%20the%20engineering%20team%20for%20Apple's%20browser%20app%2C%20Safari%2C%20said%20during%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20system%20would%20%26quot%3Bagentically%20take%20action%20on%20your%20behalf.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20already%20alerts%20users%20when%20a%20saved%20password%20is%20weak%2C%20reused%2C%20or%20may%20have%20been%20exposed%20in%20a%20data%20breach.%20The%20coming%20feature%20goes%20a%20step%20further%2C%20Apple%20said%2C%20by%20allowing%20users%20to%20change%20a%20compromised%20password%20with%20a%20single%20tap%20on%20a%20blue%20button%20on%20the%20Security%20page%20within%20the%20Passwords%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Passwords%20app%20works%20with%20Apple's%20AI%2C%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20and%20Safari%20to%20navigate%20websites%2C%20sign%20in%2C%20and%20upgrade%20passwords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222834%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shot%20of%20an%20Apple%20iPhone's%20security%20page.%20It's%20showing%20the%20user%20that%20three%20apps%20%E2%80%94%20Quantum%20College%20Hospital%2C%20Summit%20Industrial%2C%20and%20Book%20Shoppe%20%E2%80%94%20have%20compromised%20passwords.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28143c67142ea6832cdc57%3F